    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54B32 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies. This example boasts a pristine mechanical record with documented rod bearing replacement and comprehensive subframe reinforcement. The double-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, ensuring linear power delivery and crisp throttle response up to the 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via the Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains stock but has been refreshed with OEM bushings to maintain the chassis's legendary telepathic feedback. A turn-key, investment-quality specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
