      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its factory-fresh allure. The exterior features a flawless, deep-gloss finish protected by a multi-layer ceramic coating, with absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in 'as-new' condition; the premium leather still carries its original scent, and every surface\u2014from the door sills to the headliner\u2014is pristine. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive, documented service history performed exclusively by authorized technicians. It drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot. Included are all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom car cover. This is a rare opportunity to own a specimen that is indistinguishable from new.",
