      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolute mint condition\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been pampered, garage-kept, and looks absolutely stunning inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect and drives like a dream, you\u2019ve found it! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
